N IN HELL FOREVER♥ </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > And in the meantime you can get to know the cutest and the deadliest denizens of Hell: usurpers, dictators and even the chairwoman of the Central Committee of the CPSU. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hitler and Stalin</strong> are lonely at the 8-th circle of Hell waiting for the Last Judgment. Get to know them better and reveal the motives of their actions during their lives on Earth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/d21d27cabf9eadedda061308e2ac307f.poster.avif?t=1762714346\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/d21d27cabf9eadedda061308e2ac307f.webm?t=1762714346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/d21d27cabf9eadedda061308e2ac307f.mp4?t=1762714346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>♥FEATURES♥:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A hellish love story in a Christian setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Classic visual novel with a Match3 gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 11 vivid Live2d animations </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Animated 3d backgrounds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Branching story with multiple endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Excellent Lofi hip hop by the mind-blowing G374 and the masterly smth.nothing ♥</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/87fcff5d73bad7068219e9c44fad15d0.webp?t=1762714346\" width=616 height=10 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >